Uses of Package
suncertify.model

Packages that use suncertify.model
suncertify.facade Contains classes for performing complex business. 
suncertify.model Modeling for contractors information in a persistence storage is performed by this package classes. 
suncertify.model.db Modeling for contractors information exists in a database file is performed by this package classes. 
suncertify.ui.client Provides UI classes for client application. 
 

Classes in suncertify.model used by suncertify.facade
Contractor
          Encapsulates single contractor entity information to be persisted or currently resides in a persistence storage.

          Defines a model for persisting contractor entities in a persistence storage.
